Hanania okoro weche mag miriambo


1  

E higano, e due mar abich mar higa mar ang’wen mar loch Zedekia ruodh Juda, Hanania janabi, ma wuod Azur ja-Gibeon, nowuoyo gi Jeremia e Hekalu kowachone e nyim jodolo kod ji, 
2  ni Ruoth Nyasaye Manyalo Gik Moko Duto kendo ma Nyasach Israel owacho kama: “Aseturo jok mar ruodh Babulon, 
3  kendo ka pok higni ariyo orumo, to abiro dwoko gik lemo duto mane ruoth Nebukadnezar okawo motero Babulon. 
4  Bende abiro duogo Jekonia wuod Jehoyakim ma ruodh Juda kaachiel gi jo-Juda mane odar moter Babulon e tuech. Adier, abiro turo jok mar ruodh Babulon. An Ruoth Nyasaye ema awacho kamano.” 
5  To Jeremia janabi nodwoko Hanania janabi e nyim jodolo gi ji duto mane oyudo ochung’ e Hekalu, 
6  kowacho niya, “Mad Ruoth Nyasaye tim kamano! Dang’ bed maber ka omiyo wecheni duto otimore, mi oduogo gik lemo duto mane oter Babulon, kaachiel gi joma ne odar mi oter kuno e tuech! 
7  To in Hanania, kaachiel gi ji duto, winjuru gima awachonu. 
8  Jonabi machon mane okwongonwa ne koro wach ni lweny gi kech kod tuo biro biro kuom ogendini mang’eny gi pinje marateke. 
9  To ubiro ng’eyo ka janabi ma koro wach kue en janabi ma Ruoth Nyasaye oseoro adier, mana ka gik ma okoro otimore.”


10  Bang’ mano, Hanania nogolo jok e ng’ut Jeremia, moturo matindo tindo. 
11  Eka nowacho e nyim ji duto niya, “Ruoth Nyasaye osewacho ni kaka aseturo jokni e kaka obiro turo jok ma ruoth Nebukadnezar oseketo e ng’ut ogendini, kendo obiro timo kamano kapok higni ariyo orumo.”


12  To bang’ kinde moko, kane Hanania oseturo jok mane nie ng’ut Jeremia, Ruoth Nyasaye nowacho ni Jeremia 
13  mondo odhi onyis Hanania niya, “Ruoth Nyasaye osewacho ni inyalo turo jok mar yien, to obiro keto jok mar nyinyo kare. 
14  Ruoth Nyasaye Manyalo Gik Moko Duto kendo ma Nyasach Israel osewacho ni obiro keto jok mar nyinyo kuom ogendini duto, kendo giniti ni Nebukadnezar ruodh Babulon. Bende osewacho ni obiro miyo kata mana le mae bungu ti ni Nebukadnezar.”


15  Bang’e Jeremia nowacho ni Hanania niya, “Koro winji, Hanania. Ruoth Nyasaye ok oori, to imiyo jogi geno mana miriambo. 
16  Omiyo Ruoth Nyasaye owuon wacho ni obiro tieki e wang’ pinyni, nimar ibiro tho ka pok higani orumo, nikech isejiwo ji mondo otamre mako chikne.”


17  Kamano Hanania janabi notho e due mar abiriyo mar higano.

